        "share_text": "yesterday we had the privilege of visiting our friends @aconhunter to donate the last of our fundraising efforts for the year.\n\nwe\u00e2\u0080\u0099re thrilled to announce (with your help) that we\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve raised a total of $3781.18 for ACON Hunter! these folks do so much good work in the LGBQTI+ community and where proud to support them wherever possible \u00e2\u009d\u00a4\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u009c\u00a8\n\nthank you, so so much to all the venues, sponsors, hosts and our good friends @theoak.tigheshill who made this possible for 2025!\n\nwe\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll be back in 2026 with another host of events that you can get involved in, watch this space!\n\n#strengthisforeveryone #strongfriends",
