        "share_text": "HOW DO WE RATE JOSH\u00e2\u0080\u0099S FORM?? \n\nAre you gym-curious? Wanting to start a bit of a health kick in a comfortable space, while also incorporating beer? Gym Stuff for Non-Gym People might be the event you\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve been looking for\u00e2\u0080\u00a6\n\nOn Monday, December 22nd from 11am\u00e2\u0080\u009312pm, the team from Valkyrie Gym will turn the Oak into a place of exercise, teaching basic and practical gym techniques to the soundtrack of music by DJ Bonnie Ann.\n\nYou\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll get a free @younghenrys Young or @heapsnormal on arrival, and you\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll leave with a four-week exercise plan to carry you through the holidays.\n\nPerfect excuse to skip work for the day!\n\nTickets are $30 with proceeds going to @aconhunter . Hit the link in bio to grab a ticket!",
