      "content": "Valkyrie sent an attachment.",
      "share": {
        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DRUA4DsE7yQ/?carousel_share_child_media_id=3770642640267361424_4546595342",
        "share_text": "\u00f0\u009f\u0094\u008aFUNDRAISER ANNOUNCEMENT \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u008a\n\nOn the 22nd of December, we\u00e2\u0080\u0099re taking over @theoak.tigheshill to run our very first \u00e2\u0080\u009cGym Stuff For Non-Gym Folks\u00e2\u0080\u009d charity event!\n\n\u00e2\u009c\u00a8 Learn new skills using nothing but your own body and some creative \u00e2\u0080\u009cweights\u00e2\u0080\u009d supplied by our friends behind the bar!\n\n\u00e2\u009c\u00a8 Lean into the \u00e2\u0080\u009choly trinity\u00e2\u0080\u009d of wholesome community\u00e2\u0080\u00a6beers, weights and dad jokes!\n\n\u00e2\u009c\u00a8 Share a beer with your mates and call it a workout!\n\n\u00e2\u009c\u00a8 Receive a DIY 4-week \u00e2\u0080\u009cat home\u00e2\u0080\u009d program to take home after the event!\n\nOur fun yet educational \u00e2\u0080\u009cworkout\u00e2\u0080\u009d will run for 30 mins (beer in hand) followed by food and drinks supplied by The Oak and is totally appropriate for any skill level!\n\nTickets are \u00e2\u0080\u009cpay what you can\u00e2\u0080\u009d but have a suggested price of $30. All proceeds go towards our friends at @aconhunter to help them connect more folks to vital health services.\n\nBook in now to save your spot to this once in a lifetime event (link on the bio \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u0097)\n\n#gsfngf #strengthisforeveryone #strongfriends",
